Package civitas.celestis.object

Class BaseObject

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.object.BaseObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Movable, Physical, Placeable, Renderable, Tickable, Unique
Direct Known Subclasses:
ComponentObject, ImmovableObject
public class BaseObject extends Object implements Unique, Movable, Physical, Renderable, Tickable
The base class for objects in Moebius.
